# ⚙️ Project Workflow

```text
              EEG Dataset (.set)
                     │
                     ▼
          Load EEG using MNE-Python
                     │
                     ▼
          Bandpass Filtering (1–50 Hz)
                     │
                     ▼
      Multichannel EEG Signal Visualization
                     │
                     ▼
       Power Spectral Density (PSD)
                     │
                     ▼
          EEG Feature Extraction
                     │
                     ▼
      Subject-wise Brain Activity Analysis
                     │
                     ▼
      Heatmap Generation Across Subjects
                     │
                     ▼
             PCA Visualization
                     │
                     ▼
            t-SNE Visualization
                     │
                     ▼
 Machine Learning / Deep Learning Models
                     │
                     ▼
 Brain Disease Classification & Explainability
```

