> **Note:** The EEG dataset is **not included** in this repository due to its size. Download the dataset separately from OpenNeuro before running the project.

---

# 🚀 Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/Brain-Disease-Classification-EEG.git
```

Install the required dependencies:

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Update the dataset path in the source code before execution.

---

# ▶️ Running the Project

```bash
python final.py
```

All generated visualizations and analysis results will be stored inside the **outputs/** directory.

